    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously cared for\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for that 'brand new' experience without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
