      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, has been maintained to the highest professional standards. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from a showroom model, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and character.",
      "price": 48500.0,
