    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains uncompromisingly rigid, with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and conrod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this example exhibits zero paint oxidation and retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. A true driver\u2019s machine in collector-grade condition.",
